{
  "texts": [
    "This step was necessary because we had multiple GPT reappraisals per vignette, but each human participant never reappraised a vignette more than once.",
    "As such, we had six subsets of the EXPLORING HUMAN AND AI EMOTIONAL SUPPORT data, one for each vignette.",
    "Each subset thus consisted of one GPT reappraisal and the rest of the human reappraisals for a single vignette.",
    "Within each subset, we assigned percentile ranks to each reappraisal based on their mean rating.",
    "We then saved the six GPT percentile ranks."
  ]
}